-- KamiLib --

1. Features

- OpenGL and WM context creation. (complete, platform-dependant)
- Platform independant I/O (TODO)
- Basic blit and sprite functionallity (complete)
- GLSL support (complete)
- GL matrix and geometry automation (complete)
- Sound (TODO)
- Lua scripting of events and interop (partial)

